<HEADLINE>
<P>
THE NUMBERS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Animal rights movement: The Times received 34 letters in response to its 
editorial "Animals or Humans?" (April 27). Thirty readers disagreed with the 
editorial and four supported it. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA050790-0010 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 215102 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
May 7, 1990, Monday, Home Edition 
