<HEADLINE>
<P>
BATTLING THE MEDFLY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The state Department of Food and Agriculture will conduct aerial spraying of 
malathion beginning at 9 p.m., weather permitting. 
</P>
<P>
Area: 27 square miles in two separate areas encompassing parts of parts of 
Arleta, Burbank, Granada Hills, North Hollywood, Panorma City, Sepulveda, Sun 
Valley, Van Nuys, Hancock Park and parts of Koreatown, Country Club Park and 
Mid-City. 
</P>
<P>
Precautions: Stay indoors; keep animals indoors; wash animal dishes and toys 
left outside; cover cars; keep doors and windows closed. 
</P>
<P>
Information: Toll-free numbers for the Agricultural Commissioner: (800) 
356-2894; (800) 225-1346. 
</P>
