ESCAPES; REED, FRANK HERBERT; HEZBOLLAH; PRISONERS -- ISRAEL; SHIITE MUSLIMS; 
UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- ISRAEL; UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN 
RELATIONS -- IRAN; UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- SYRIA; HOSTAGES -- 
HEALTH 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
